position: absolute;
width: 3rem;
height: 3rem;
border-radius: 50%;
display: flex;
cursor: pointer;
bottom: 8px;
right: 8px;
img {
width: 2.8rem;
height: 2.8rem;
}
&:hover {
background: var(--main-color);
.basket-hover-box {
opacity: 1;
}
}
}
.basket-img {
width: 22px;
height: 22px;
} // line 212
.basket-img {
width: 30px;
height: 30px;
} // line 245 — duplicate!
.basket-hover-box {
position: absolute;
opacity: 0;
}
/* + responsive overrides at lines 390, 430 */addToBasket() {
const id = this.basketViewService.basketId
if (!id) {
this.addItemToTheBasket(); return
}
this.basketService.getBasket(id).subscribe({ … })
}THE COST OF SEPARATION: The button is defined in three files and held together by the magic strings “add-to-basket-button” , “basket-img” , “basket-hover-box” . Rename a class in the HTML and the style silently stops applying. The styles
